HEADWORD: Flower State
<hw>Flow"er State</hw>. <def>Florida; -- a nickname, alluding to sense
of L. <xex>floridus</xex>, from <xex>florida</xex> flowery. See
<er>Florid</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
